  27 Feb 2005; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> :
  Fixed sed'ing of scripts. Should actually fix #81633.

  23 Feb 2005; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org>
  drscheme-208.ebuild:
  Marked 208 as stable, which fixes #81633.

